contentNode.address: PO Box 93725, Yas Island, Abu Dhabi, UAE
contentNode.locationDescrpition:
Park Inn by Radisson Hotel Abu Dhabi Yas Island is a smart and fuss-free urban retreat. Located at Yas Island, the hotel offers bright and spacious rooms with stunning panoramic views of the Arabian Gulf, golf course, and Yas Marina Circuit. The trendy décor and modern facilities are suited for the new generation of travellers who love a hassle-free, personalized and “Feel Good” hotel experience.
The interior of all 204 rooms & suites is fresh and modern with more focus towards sleek fittings and space. Apple TV, complimentary high-speed WiFi, and state-of-the-art headboards with colour-changing LED mood lights complete the “cool” guest experience.

P.O. Box 93725
Abu Dhabi

contentNode.locationDescrpition: Sparkling views of the Arabian Gulf and easy access to the marina, Yas Beach and Yas Links, make the Radisson Blu a beautifully situated as well as wonderfully luxurious hotel. And with numerous restaurants and bars and a full-service spa with five treatment rooms, it has everything you need for a beautifully relaxing break. The Radisson Blu Hotel has three restaurants and two bars – offering a range of international favourites. If it’s Italian you fancy, there’s the mouth-watering cuisine of Filini, or if you’re in the mood for some Belgian bites, there’s the Belgian Beer Café. For a broader selection from around the globe, visit Assymetri, which is where you’ll also find the famous Super Breakfast Buffet, being served daily.

The hotel is connected to the Yas Marina Circuit with easy access to a wide range of attractions including theme parks, shopping malls, a golf course, beach and a marina.
